= Linball game =

Linball (Linux Pinball) is an open source pinball simulation. Use the touchscreen to control the flippers.

[[Image:linball-neo.png]]
[[Image:linball-neo2.png]]

Here you see Linball running on a Neo: 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P5cycCaEdl0

== Download ==
New 0.2 version:
http://linball.sf.net/linball-openmoko_0.2_armv4t.opk

== Installation ==
Make sure that you have installed the latest version of SDL libraries :
libsdl, libsdl-gfx, libsdl-image, libsdl-mixer, libsdl-ttf, libsdl-x11 and libogg.

<tt>opkg install http://linball.sf.net/linball-openmoko_0.2_armv4t.opk</tt>

 
